                    2,
                    "secret or token")
    );

    @Override
    public ValidationResult validate(SkillPackageContext context) {
        List<String> errors = new ArrayList<>();

        for (PackageEntry entry : context.entries()) {
            if (!isTextLike(entry.path())) {
